@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF

package "DashBoard-Dev 服务" {
  [Controller 层] as Controller
  [Service 层] as Service
  [Nacos代理客户端] as Proxy
}

package "外部依赖" {
  [Nacos 配置中心] as Nacos
  [业务应用集群] as Apps
}

package "前端界面" {
  [管理界面] as UI
}

UI --> Controller : HTTP 请求
Controller --> Service : 业务调用
Service --> Proxy : 代理调用
Proxy --> Nacos : HTTP API
Service --> Apps : 直接 HTTP 调用

note right of Proxy
  **核心职责：**
  • 封装 Nacos HTTP API
  • 处理命名空间转换
  • 统一异常处理
  • 提供配置 CRUD 操作
end note

@enduml